  <brief_title>Peri-procedural Smoking Cessation Program in Patients With Chronic Pain</brief_title>
  <official_title>Implementation of a Peri-procedural Smoking Cessation Program in Patients With Chronic Pain Undergoing Interventional Pain Management Procedures</official_title>
